**###Before Save###**taskrefno = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO") bktype = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_DETAIL_UDF2") bktypelist = Array("CHAPTER 11","CHAPTER 13") taskstatus = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_STATUS") taskcompletedate = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_COMPLETED") pacerverifiedstatuses = array("BK-ACTIVE","BK-DISMISSED","BK-DISCHARGED")
If NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF24") = "CHECK" Then If Ubound(filter(pacerverifiedstatuses,taskstatus,True,1)) = -1 then NLSApp.Messagebox("Invalid Task Status (" & taskstatus & ") for Pacer Verified." & chr(10) & "Save Aborted." & chr(10) & "Please select a valid task Status.") 'NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET status_code_id = " & TEMPLATE_STATUS_BK_FILED & " WHERE task_refno = " & NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO")) 'NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus taskrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"ADD" NLSApp.Break() End If Else If Ubound(filter(pacerverifiedstatuses,taskstatus,True,1)) = 0 then 'YES/NO Box add here msgprompt = "Selected Task Status (" & taskstatus & ") requires Pacer Verified box to be checked." & chr(10) & chr(10) & "Check Box? (Y/N)" If NLSApp.YesNoMessageBox(msgprompt) Then NLSapp.SetField "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24","CHECK" Else NLSApp.Messagebox("Save Aborted." & chr(10) & "Please select a valid task Status or CANCEL.") NLSApp.Break() NLSApp.RefreshScreen() End If End If End if**###Before Save###****###Before Activate###**bktype = NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2") bktypelist = Array("CHAPTER 11","CHAPTER 13")
'Field colors ' NLSapp.SetFieldAttribute "TASK_DETAIL_UDF16", RGB(0,0,0), RGB(255,248,220), true
'Hide fields 'Proof of Claim If isdate(NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF12")) = True Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF19", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF20", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF21", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF30", False End if
'BK type is 11 or 13 for each x in bktypelist if x = bktype Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF13", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF14", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF15", False End if next
'Enable fields 'List of Creditors If Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF17") = "YES" Then NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF18", false End if
NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", False
If Not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If Not IsDate(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF3")) = False Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF6")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again.") If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF22")) = 0 Then 'NLSapp.MessageBox("A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked." & Chr(13) & "Please try again." NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If **###Before Activate###****###Before Create###****###Before Create###****###On Delete###****###On Delete###****###After Save###**taskrefno = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_REFNO") loanrefno = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_NLS_REFNO") bktype = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_DETAIL_UDF2") bktypelist = Array("CHAPTER 11","CHAPTER 13") taskstatus = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_STATUS") taskcompletedate = NLSapp.GetField( "TASK_COMPLETED") pacerverified = NLSapp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF24") pacerverifiedstatuses = array("BK-ACTIVE","BK-INVALID","BK-DISMISSED","BK-DISCHARGED")
'Hide fields 'Proof of Claim If isdate(NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF12")) = True Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF19", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF20", false NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF21", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF30", False End if
'BK type is 11 or 13 for each x in bktypelist if x = bktype Then NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF13", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF14", False NLSapp.HideFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF15", False End if next
'Enable fields 'List of Creditors If Not NLSApp.getField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF17") = "YES" Then NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF18", false End if
'pacer check box (UDF24) before verifying Pacer can be enabled to check NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", False
If Not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF2")) = 0 Then 'A Bankruptcy type must be selected If Not IsDate(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF3")) = False Then 'Date filed must be entered If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF6")) = 0 Then 'A Court must be selected If not len(NLSApp.GetField("TASK_DETAIL_UDF22")) = 0 Then 'A Case # must be entered NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
'----TASKSTATUS vs LOANSTATUS validations--------
If pacerverified = "CHECK" Then If taskcompletedate = "" Then taskcompletedate = DateFormat(NOW(),111) End if Select Case taskstatus Case "BK-DISCHARGED" Select Case bktype Case "CHAPTER 7" bkstatus = LOAN_STATUS_BK_DISCHARGE7 Case "CHAPTER 11" bkstatus = LOAN_STATUS_BK_DISCHARGE11 Case "CHAPTER 12" bkstatus = LOAN_STATUS_BK_DISCHARGE12 Case "CHAPTER 13" bkstatus = LOAN_STATUS_BK_DISCHARGE13 End Select NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),bkstatus,"ADD" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_GL_CHARGE_OFF,"ADD" NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET completion_date = '" & taskcompletedate & "' WHERE task_refno = " & taskrefno)
Case "BK-INVALID" , "BK-DISMISSED" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"DELETE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"DELETE" NLSapp.SQLSelectStatement("SELECT 0; UPDATE task SET completion_date = '" & taskcompletedate & "' WHERE task_refno = " & taskrefno)
Case "BK-ACTIVE" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_ACTIVE,"ADD" NLSApp.SetSecondaryLoanStatus loanrefno,NOW(),LOAN_STATUS_BK_NOTICE,"DELETE"
End Select
End if NLSApp.RefreshScreen()**###After Save###****###After Create###****###After Create###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###On Add Button Clicked###****###Local Functions###**Function DateFormat(datestring,formatcode)
If IsDate(datestring) = true Then If len(DAY(datestring)) = 1 Then daytext = "0" & DAY(datestring) Else daytext = DAY(datestring) End if
If len(MONTH(datestring)) = 1 Then mnthtext = "0" & MONTH(datestring) Else mnthtext = MONTH(datestring) End if
Select case formatcode 'U.S. = mm/dd/yyyy case 1 DateFormat = mnthtext &"/"& daytext &"/"& Right(YEAR(datestring),2)
case 101 DateFormat = mnthtext &"/"& daytext &"/"& YEAR(datestring)
'JAPAN = yyyy/mm/dd case 11 DateFormat = Right(YEAR(datestring),2) &"/"& mnthtext &"/"& daytext case 111 DateFormat = YEAR(datestring)&"/"& mnthtext &"/"& daytext
'Default with Day and timestamp removed = mon yyyy case 10077 DateFormat = MonthName(Month(datestring), False) & " " & YEAR(datestring)
Case Else
DateFormat = -1
End Select
Else
DateFormat = -1
End if
End Function
Sub PacerVerification (bktype,filedt,courtval,caseno,pacercheckyn,taskrefno) 'Evaluates 4 fields and if any are not filled, it will not enable a field (usredef24) for editing If Not len(bktype) = 0 Then 'A Bankruptcy type must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked If Not IsDate(filedt) = False Then 'Date filed must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked If not len(courtval) = 0 Then 'A Court must be selected before verifying Pacer can be checked. If not len(caseno) = 0 Then 'A Case # must be entered before verifying Pacer can be checked. NLSapp.EnableFields "TASK_DETAIL_UDF24", True End If End If End If End If
End sub**###Local Functions###**
